Title: Zanzibar Riots, 1961
Summary: Zanzibar Protectorate Commission of Inquiry into Civil Disturbances on 1st June 1961 and Succeeding Days, held at the Legislative Council Chamber, Zanzibar, before Sir Stafford Foster-Sutton (Chairman), Sir Vincent Tewson, C.A. Grossmith, commencing on Monday, 25th September 1961 / note taken by Treasury Reporter.
